raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Caleb: Morning!
Caleb: Hope the task went by smoothly!
Caleb: Naomi has been telling me she had a good time!
Player: Glad to hear it
Caleb: She's been bragging about some pictures she can't share yet 😅
Caleb: So I imagine it was a breeze and that you did well!
Caleb: I'm expecting you're getting your invite this Saturday then!
Player: Oh really? That's great to hear!
Player: How did Mabel's application task go?
Caleb: Oh right, it went well
Caleb: I can't disclose the picture or details about the picture but
Caleb: I took this myself, I wanted to share with you
Caleb: img: mabel/79
Caleb: It came out pretty well!
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Caleb: Mabel... has certain charms to her I never expected 😅
	Caleb: I mean I knew she was pretty but...
	- You can tell me exactly what you think
		Player: You can tell me exactly what you think
		Caleb: Really?
		Caleb: I don't want to cross any boundaries here
		Player: Don't worry, we're all friends
		Caleb: Really? If you say so then 😳
		Caleb: I think she could do some modeling too for the club
		Player: Really?
		Caleb: Yeah, I actually kept getting distracted
		Caleb: I almost forgot what we were doing 😆
		Caleb: If you'd like, you could suggest it to her
		Player: I'll see!
	- I get the gist of it
		Player: I get the gist of it
		Player: A lot of guys probably find her attractive
		Caleb: That's probably true
		Caleb: You're a lucky guy!
		Player: Thanks! 😁
else:
	Caleb: She was very well composed!
	Caleb: She focused on her task and had a natural talent for it
	Player: Really?
	Caleb: Totally! And she wouldn't stop talking about you
	Caleb: Where we went seemed to remind her a lot about somewhere you grew up together!
	Caleb: It was so heartwarming tbh!
	Player: That's my Mabel for ya haha
	Caleb: She's endearing! 👍
Caleb: Alright I gotta run
Caleb: Have a few last minute things to take care of!
Player: Take care!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
